DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260411T140000
SUMMARY:April Neptune Diner Meetup!
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Freethought Society\nWe will be meeting for brunch a
 t a local diner! This one is a bit later than usual for those who like to 
 sleep in!\n\nNeptune Diner\n924 N. Prince St.\nLancaster PA 17603\n\nNeptu
 ne Diner is on the right side of the one-way Prince St. It has its own siz
 able parking lot adjacent. If you pass the Baseball stadium you've gone to
 o far!\n\nWe look forward to seeing you!
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-freethought-society/events/
 313902536/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260322T230749Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260322T230749Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Lancaster Freethought Society
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-freethought-society/
UID:event_308585161@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260407T030138Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260419T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260419T120000
SUMMARY:LFS Coffee & Convo  
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Freethought Society\nThe Coffee and Convo meetup is 
 always on the 3rd Sunday of the Month at 9am.\n\nWe will meet at Centervil
 le Diner\, 100 S. Centerville Rd.\n\nMeet up with fellow freethinkers to t
 alk\, eat or just have a warm or cold beverage of your choice. This is usu
 ally a small intimate meeting. It's about casual conversation and getting 
 to know your fellow freethinkers.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-freethought-society/events/
 308585161/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20250621T185228Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20250621T185228Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Lancaster Freethought Society
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-freethought-society/
UID:event_308585166@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260407T030138Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260506T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260506T210000
SUMMARY:LFS Monthly Discussion - El Serrano's
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Freethought Society\nCome joins us for intelligent d
 iscussion and freethinking fun at our monthly meeting. Lancaster Freethoug
 ht Society is a community for Freethinkers\, Atheists\, Agnostics\, Humani
 sts\, Non-believers\, Skeptics\, and those who are simply curious. There i
 s no fee to attend our meetings which range from topical subjects of inter
 est to freethinkers such as Church/State Separation\, as well as subjects 
 such as science\, philosophy\, ethics\, counter-apologetics\, and psycholo
 gy. All are welcome to attend no matter what your beliefs may be but prose
 lytizing is not allowed. Bring your articles\, news\, jokes\, gripes\, que
 stions\, ideas\, topics\, or anything else you would like to discuss with 
 the rest of the group.\n\nHope to see you there!
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-freethought-society/events/
 308585166/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20250621T185239Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20250621T185239Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
